  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Ferro Concepts FCPC V5 插板胸挂 (黑色军团)",
      "en": "Ferro Concepts FCPC V5 Plate Carrier (Black Division)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "FCPC V5",
      "en": "FCPC V5"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "第五代 FCPC 插板胸挂延续了 Ferro Concepts 公司打造轻量化自适应装备的设计理念。新一代产品进一步完善了插板背心和其延伸部分的剪裁，以提升穿戴舒适度与机动能力。狼棕色版本。配有 2 具无线电手台，分别用于联络下属小队以及总部。",
      "en": "The fifth-generation FCPC plate carrier continues Ferro Concepts’ focus on lightweight, adaptable gear. In this version, the plate bags and carrier contour have been redesigned for improved comfort and mobility. Coyote Brown version. Equipped with two radios for communicating with both the assigned squad and HQ."
    },
